@RandySheriffH, could you take a look at the compile error in topk cuda kernel. The cause could be related to some update in cub in CUDA 11.6 and how cub is used in topk kernel.
FWIW same error with VS2019. It doesn't seem to be specific to the TopK kernel though - that's just the first one that reports an error. If you attempt another build a lot of other kernels fail.
